</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<div> </div>
<h2><a name="Itinerary"></a>Itinerary</h2>
<p><strong>Day 1 (Monday or Friday)</strong> Fly to Bergen airport and transfer to <a data-udi="umb://document/a09d8dda0d4f48d68be229cdaeb2f377" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a09d8dda0d4f48d68be229cdaeb2f377}" title="Balestrand">Balestrand</a> on the Sognefjord, known as ‘King of the Fjords’ for being the longest and deepest fjord in Norway and stretching over 200km. Exploring this fjord is a real treat with an opportunity to enjoy picturesque boat trips, gentle walking routes along the shore, the impressive Jøstedal glacier and the world’s steepest gauge railway from Flåm.</p>
<p><strong>Day 4 or 5 (Friday or Monday) </strong>A spectacular 3 hour drive over the magical Gauler mountains to <a data-udi="umb://document/14f6ab787ad2493ab23ce60aa9f14e6a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/14f6ab787ad2493ab23ce60aa9f14e6a}" title="Loen">Loen</a> on the Nordfjord, your base for the next 3 or 4 nights. Trips to the famous Geiranger Fjord or to the emerald lakes and ice-blue glaciers of the Lodal and Briksdal valleys are a must and the new Skylift cable-car from the village provides further exploring opportunities with several walking trails at the top, not to mention the views. The spa and pool facilities at the <a data-udi="umb://document/fbdb2d63e0f24d7fb8fbb7a20fdd9578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fbdb2d63e0f24d7fb8fbb7a20fdd9578}" title="Alexandra Hotel">Hotel Alexandra</a> provide a great setting to relax and unwind after your day out.</p>
<p><strong>Day 8 (Monday or Friday) </strong>Another scenic transfer to the vibrant Art Nouveau city of <a data-udi="umb://document/4796d8535a46439d92020f8a158e7c03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4796d8535a46439d92020f8a158e7c03}" title="Alesund">Ålesund</a> allows you to sit back and admire the spectacular scenery of the Nordfjord and Sunnmøre regions up close. Once in Ålesund, explore its museums, discover its interesting architecture and surrounding islands or simply take a stroll along its pretty waterfront.</p>
<p><strong>Day 11 or 12 (Friday or Monday) </strong>Return by shuttle to Ålesund airport for your flight back to the UK. </p>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>What’s included</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Return flight from the UK to Bergen and back from Ålesund</li>
<li>Scenic transfers to and from the airport and between each resort*</li>
<li>Accommodation with private facilities throughout</li>
<li>Half board meals included in Balestrand (Hotel Kviknes only) &amp; Loen and Ulvik if extending to 14 nights</li>
<li>Bed &amp; Breakfast in Ålesund &amp; Balestrand (Hotel Midtnes only) and Bergen if extending to 14 nights</li>
<li>'Meet &amp; Greet' service throughout your stay, with a welcome to the resort and 24/7 phone service</li>
</ul>
<p><em>*For guests arriving into Bergen on indirect flights via Amsterdam, transfers from Bergen airport to Balestrand will be by minibus. For all other guests, transfers will be by coastal express boat (transfer from airport to boat quay included)</em></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>Departure dates &amp; prices</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Depart on any date throughout the summer, as long as it's a Monday or Friday</li>
<li>Monday departures = 11 nights = <span>4 nights Balestrand, 3 nights Loen, 4 nights Ålesund</span></li>
<li><span>Friday departures = </span>10 nights = <span>3 nights Balestrand, 4 nights Loen, 3 nights Ålesund</span></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>Your Hotels</strong></p>
<p><strong>Accommodation: </strong>Guests will have a choice of either 'standard' hotels or 'superior' hotels.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Hotels</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Balestrand</strong>  <a data-udi="umb://document/e6e72ed8f54b4b799df9821bf732b69d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e6e72ed8f54b4b799df9821bf732b69d}" title="Midtnes Hotel">Hotel Midtnes</a> ★★+</li>
<li><strong>Loen</strong>  <a data-udi="umb://document/7780b99803294b0f8a9519ed836b9830" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7780b99803294b0f8a9519ed836b9830}" title="Loenfjord Hotel">Hotel Loenfjord</a> ★★★+</li>
<li><strong>Ålesund</strong>  <a data-udi="umb://document/89e354afa6824ae197da03b9604055e7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89e354afa6824ae197da03b9604055e7}" title="First Hotel Atlantica">First Hotel Atlantica</a> ★★★+</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Superior Hotels </strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Balestrand</strong>  <a data-udi="umb://document/d26dcba440054402b9ccfe7166c1ad56" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d26dcba440054402b9ccfe7166c1ad56}" title="Kviknes Hotel">Hotel Kviknes</a> ★★★★</li>
<li><strong>Loen</strong>   <a href="/{localLink:umb://document/fbdb2d63e0f24d7fb8fbb7a20fdd9578}" title="Alexandra Hotel">Hotel Alexandra</a> ★★★★+</li>
<li><strong>Ålesund</strong>  <a href="/{localLink:umb://document/7ce188510b05444696b765f7f5cc643b}" title="Hotel Brosundet">Hotel Brosundet</a> ★★★★</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>Departure flights to Bergen from:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Gatwick &amp; Aberdeen</li>
<li>Or indirect flights via Amsterdam from regional airports available on request</li>
<li>Flight supplements may apply</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
